{
  "mcpServers": {
    "chrome-devtools": {
      "command": "npx", "args": ["-y", "chrome-devtools-mcp@latest"]
    }
  }
}
``` Servers are **lazy by default** — they won't connect until you actually call one of their tools. The adapter caches   ...    ```json
